Get the municipalities (kommuner) in a county (län)

Source: R/SersVix.R
sers_vix_kommuner.Rd

This function returns the municipalities (kommuner) in a county (län) in Sweden. The parameter lan must be a valid county (län) in Sweden.

sers_vix_kommuner(lan)

Arguments

lan

A character string with the name of a county (län) in Sweden

Value

A vector of type character containing names of municipalities (kommuner) in the county (län)

See also

Description of https://www.slu.se/en/departments/aquatic-resources1/databases/database-for-testfishing-in-streams/, description of API https://dvfisk.slu.se/swagger/index.html

Other SersVix API functions: sers_vix_huvudavrinningsomraden(), sers_vix_lan(), sers_vix_rapport()

Examples

# This example will access the Internet to get the data and will not work offline
kommuner <- sers_vix_kommuner("Västra Götaland")
kommuner
